longBusinessSummary: Fuji Offset Plates Manufacturing Ltd engages in the manufacture and trading of gravure printing cylinders and related services in the printing industry Singapore, Malaysia, and internationally. The company operates through Printing Cylinders and Investment in Property Development Companies segments. It sells pre-sensitized offset and CTP plates; and supplies related industry required chemicals. The company is also involved in letting of properties. In addition, it invests in commercial, industrial, hospitality, residential, and/or mixed development properties. Fuji Offset Plates Manufacturing Ltd was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in Singapore.
